{"tid":2218116,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"世衛：台灣已加入全球採購疫苗平台","createTime":"2020-09-26T03:42:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T03:45:06.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"16ea8669b7baadf6d881090f626a0e3de900aa85","tid":2218116,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T03:42:41.000Z","msg":"世衛證實，台灣已經加入全球採購疫苗平台COVAX，有望購入新型冠狀病毒疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n世衛總幹事高級顧問艾爾沃德表示，目前共159個國家或經濟體加入平台，包括並非世衛成員的台灣。世衛並正與大陸磋商，在疫苗供應平台中扮演的角色，大陸可能會為平台供應疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n全球採購疫苗平台由世衛及另外兩個組織共同主導，目的是加快新型肺炎疫苗研發和生產，並確保世界各國和地區可公平取得疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n在台灣，衛生福利部長陳時中昨日在立法院接受立委質詢時表示，已與平台簽約，預計下月初支付訂金，又指台灣不會選擇大陸的疫苗。流行疫情指揮中心表示，台灣揀選的採購方案，在疫苗廠商選擇上有較大的主動權，目標是讓全台灣六成人口、約1358萬人接種疫苗。"},{"pid":"a98376b865a71dbed582b6e2761951144af4e502","tid":2218116,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T03:42:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551757-20200926.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551757-20200926.htm&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTu063eTsi4ka8iUmrXsVTuNg%3D&h=0dc23eb9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551757-20200926.htm&h=6e5386fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551757-20200926.htm</a>"},{"pid":"87c3fd1ea037ec23dacbbedb4a121d1881c697b6","tid":2218116,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T03:44:43.000Z","msg":"宜家有邊度真係供應到疫苗<br />\n咪話暫時大陸行最前?"},{"pid":"932f8587486410df9cb4e500676d596961a74798","tid":2218116,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T03:45:06.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">台灣不會選擇大陸的疫苗</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2730000/2731147/gov_thumb_20200821_ch_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2730000%2F2731147%2Fgov_thumb_20200821_ch_1024.jpg&h=c15ccb47&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}